00:01:08.765 --> 00:01:10.099
to some new cool ideas,

00:01:10.099 --> 00:01:12.674
it's all here to help support you along the way.

00:01:12.674 --> 00:01:16.344
Under support, you'll see community resources like FAQs,

00:01:16.344 --> 00:01:18.385
live chat, Stack Overflow,

00:01:18.385 --> 00:01:19.700
and classes you can take.

00:01:19.700 --> 00:01:23.025
There's also professional resources like partnerships,

00:01:23.025 --> 00:01:26.555
