00:01:26.555 --> 00:01:28.465
Finally, under the documentation,

00:01:28.465 --> 00:01:30.310
you'll find stuff like reference material,

00:01:30.310 --> 00:01:32.174
descriptions of important concepts,

00:01:32.174 --> 00:01:35.239
tutorials, and even more useful resources.

00:01:35.239 --> 00:01:38.949
They've made this site really intuitive for you to explore yourself.

00:01:38.950 --> 00:01:42.915
